{"tid":1866973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"意大利因應新型疫情停飛直航航班　中方不滿向意方施壓","createTime":"2020-02-07T03:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T04:04:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b90332d8e7d38d18635e88fced8436db67638d8a","tid":1866973,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:41:45.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部對意大利因應內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續，宣布暫停與兩國的直航航班，表示強烈不滿，認為意方作出過度反應和限制措施。外交部副部長秦剛其後會見意大利駐華大使，意大利同意臨時恢復兩國的部分商業航班。<br />\n<br />\n央視報道，意大利在未提前通報中方情況下，單方面停航對兩國公民旅行造成極大不便，令很多中國公民滯留意大利。中國政府將盡一切可能把滯留海外的中國公民接回家，意大利駐華大使方瀾意表示，現階段願根據中方航空公司申請，盡快批准部分民航班次往返，並積極努力恢復兩國間正常往來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507135-20200207.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507135-20200207.htm&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWWLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=b1d7cb6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507135-20200207.htm&h=3a7368b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507135-20200207.htm</a>"},{"pid":"45c44b5c47b71dee397317343707c43eb840412b","tid":1866973,"uid":82938,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:42:28.000Z","msg":"自己輸出病毒仲惡過人"},{"pid":"ef2bef677d0fdf95b24d81c2fbf91469c41451a9","tid":1866973,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"中國人死大一佢咪算"},{"pid":"2b237ab1e1bbf3235813f3628b69e68798939c81","tid":1866973,"uid":89752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"驅逐出境啦"},{"pid":"cc51c77dba49999235385d176da09c3088d2af2a","tid":1866973,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:44:36.000Z","msg":"跪？"},{"pid":"9a79ee7032b6eaed70231c0c9c87cfb3bfea6a9f","tid":1866973,"uid":39710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"仲講旅行，係咪癡鳩線